title: Surprise Team MVPs
itunes:title: Surprise Team MVPs
description:
A bunker filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler bring you all of the latest news in the NFL including more players testing positive for Covid-19 including some big name stars. Pete Carroll says he's received a phone call about Kaepernick and Mitch Trubisky is "pissed off in a good way" about competing for his job. The heroes give their surprise team MVPs for the upcoming season.
